Question: Ningbo Klinsmann Intelligent Technology Co.,Ltd. CES 2024 product highlight and specification
Summary:
Ningbo Klinsmann Intelligent Technology Co.,Ltd

Robot Vacuum Cleaner

- Offers over 15 different models including Lidar robot vacuum, Mini Robot Vacuum, Robot Vacuum With Camera, and Cheap robot vacuum
- Provides OEM/SKD/Dropshipping support and welcomes distributors
- ISO9001 & BSCI verified factory with strong R&D team and experienced workers
- Products have various certifications including CE-LVD, EC-EMC, CB, FCC, BSCI, RoHS
- Aims to be the world's leading brand in robot vacuum cleaners and cordless stick vacuum cleaners
